utils.testlink

Interface TestLinkAPIConst

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TestLinkAPIClient, TestLinkAPIHelper, TestLinkAPIResults

    public interface TestLinkAPIConst
    The constants used by the dbfacade implementation of the TestLink API. The method names and execution parameter constants can be found in this file.
